id: pm-lodl
title: "Inventory the CLI-to-core call graph: map every command to core modules and classify logic for SDK promotion"
description: "Produce the definitive map: for each of the ~60 commands, which src/core functions it calls, and which logic currently living in src/cli/commands (parsing aside) is business logic that must move behind the SDK. Output feeds both pm-usfg promotion tasks and pm-n7rr consolidation clusters. Duplicate check: no existing call-graph/inventory item."
